{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-22","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razumevanje nečije rutine, poput navika za ručak, zahteva obraćanje pažnje na konkretne detalje u razgovoru.</p>\n<p>Sofija objašnjava da kada ne može otići u kafić blizu mesta rada, obično donosi svoj ručak sa kuće, jede za svojim stolom i proverava napredak dok jede. Ovo pokazuje da njen raspored ručka može da se menja u zavisnosti od situacije, ali uvek uključuje jasan način za upravljanje svojim vremenom i radom.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-22"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta Sophie obično radi za ručak?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Uvek idem u kafić.</p>","feedback":"<p>Sophie kaže da ne ide u kafić svaki put.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ona nikada ne ruča.</p>","feedback":"<p>Nema naznaka da Sophie preskače ručak.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ponekad nosi svoj obrok na posao.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Daima anakula mezani mwake.</p>","feedback":"<p>Sophie pominje da jede za svojim stolom, ali ne svaki put.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Sophie","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"2.1-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":45.04,"finishTimestamp":49.74},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","po